skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: alpha counter
des:
Let Alexa count for you!

Just say "Alpha Counter, count to seven" and you will her Alexa counting from one to seven.
You can also specify the start number by saying "Alpha Counter, count from four to nine".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
